  "title": "<div><i>Loud VG sound effect (o.s.).</i></div>",
  "content": "<div><i>Loud VG sound effect (o.s.).</i></div>\n<div><i><br></i></div>\n<div>Dan</div>\n<div>Are you high?</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><i>Mark offers Dan a quick glare—</i></div>\n<div><i><br></i></div>\n<div><i>Dan thinks for a moment, then says;</i></div>\n<div><i><br></i></div>\n<div>Dan</div>\n<div>Oh yeah. We are high. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Mark</div>\n<div>Just forget it. I shouldn’t have brought it up. My bad. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Enrique</div>\n<div>Don’t be stupid. That’s impossible. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Hunter</div>\n<div>Out with it. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Mark</div>\n<div>Nope. Never mind. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Enrique</div>\n<div>Never mind? </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Dan</div>\n<div>Never us mind. Art thou mad?</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Mark</div>\n<div>Fine. I think you’re sick. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><i>Beat. </i></div>\n<div><i><br></i></div>\n<div>Dan</div>\n<div>Huh?</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Hunter</div>\n<div>Who?</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Enrique</div>\n<div>Me?</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Mark</div>\n<div>I think <i>you</i> are sick. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Enrique</div>\n<div>If I’m so sick, then why are we friends, huh?</div>\n<div><br></div>",
